Package <Unnamed>

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RMIApp
    The remote interface provides the Description of all methods of the remote object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CarData
    The CarData class with Getter and Setter Methods is for picking the values placed in the form fields ID, Make, Model and Year in the .fxml file and for adding the same into a table present in the same .fxml file.
    Client
    The Client Program Class fetches the remote object and invokes the required method which in this case is 'animation()'.
    dbConnection
    The dbConnection class is the class that contains the credentials to access the database.
    ImplGUI
    The remote interface 'RMIApp' is implemented here.
    ImplGUIController
    The ImplGUIController class is a controller class that does the backend work of the application.
    ImplGUIModel
    The ImplGUIModel class is to facilitate the connection of the ImplGUIController Class to the database
    Server
    The Server Program implements the remote interface 'RMIApp' and extends the implementation class 'Application'.
